/apps/broadcasting_complaint/index.aspx?lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期： 2019/6/12 時間1830 新聞報導</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f4e1f9fe4d3ebbe90e1e0e493413d4914ace11b","tid":1232642,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"c708b7fa406699835ebf62925f03a8c16170933e","tid":1232642,"uid":80072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"唔反對衝，但而家衝嚟做乜先，仲要3點人最少先衝"},{"pid":"f2abfe8d075554e037c5cf0d26f00925cbbebd47","tid":1232642,"uid":65912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:16:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/一百萬人-隨傳隨到-才是權貴最恐懼的事/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9A%A8%E5%82%B3%E9%9A%A8%E5%88%B0-%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AC%8A%E8%B2%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%2F&d=xNvf4PJMmDX7L7bksShbPtOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=fe9b793d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA-%E9%9A%A8%E5%82%B3%E9%9A%A8%E5%88%B0-%E6%89%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AC%8A%E8%B2%B4%E6%9C%80%E6%81%90%E6%87%BC%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%8B%2F&h=2f728eb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/一百萬人-隨傳隨到-才是權貴最恐懼的事/</a><br />\n和理非非唔代表無得玩"},{"pid":"4ca1fa0e8182a60dd3aaeba0b8d1369d36b1adcf","tid":1232642,"uid":145496,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"各自修行，不阻止、不篤灰！"},{"pid":"e1692e09f90413f569a90de41bdf1fe8c9db1c7f","tid":1232642,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:37:08.000Z","msg":"大家一齊推啊 啲太放晒cam 到時一有人衝 我地又會俾人屈架啦"},{"pid":"14e8ab3eca1ccdebadafdaea7bdbe0a54e62fd43","tid":1232642,"uid":135033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:38:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee25655dc850192932c1e1496c3ee42de64